CHANGES
============================================================================

Release 0.6.1 (2012-08-25)
    [FIX] Prompt validation bug.

Release 0.6.0 (2011-09-16)
    [CHR] BC break: By default do not raise SystemExit after emitting
          critical log record.

Release 0.5.3 (2011-08-15)
    [FIX] Python 2.x compatibility.

Release 0.5.2 (2011-08-11)
    [ADD] ProgressbarWidget can be used for displaying non-discrete
          progress status (BC break - use update method instead of inc).
    [ADD] Strings appended to sticky_widgets are converted to MessageWidget.

Release 0.5.1 (2011-08-07)
    [CHG] Allow alternative location of translation.

Release 0.5.0 (2011-03-16)
    [CHG] First release.